Class TrackingSystem

java.lang.Object
TrackingSystem
public class TrackingSystem extends Object
The TrackingSystem class manages a list of tracked space objects. It allows filtering, displaying, and assessing the orbital status of these objects, and can export relevant data to CSV and text files.

    • assessOrbitStatusAndExport

      public void assessOrbitStatusAndExport()
      Assesses each tracked object's orbital status and risk level. Also exports the assessment results to CSV and text files. An object is considered in orbit if it meets several conditions such as known orbit type, valid longitude, and not being too old.
